    "name": "In Your Dreams All Natural Jamaican Handmade Body Butter",
    "price": 1500.0,
    "category": "Natural Body Care",
    "description": "<p>You will never have to worry about ashy&nbsp;skin when you apply In Your Dreams all natural Jamaican handmade body butter to your skin.&nbsp;Our&nbsp;luxurious body butter was formulated with the finest natural ingredients to nourish and pamper you from head to toe.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Kokum Butter: Known for its exceptional moisturizing properties, kokum butter is deeply hydrating without leaving a greasy residue. Packed with essential fatty acids and antioxidants, it helps to rejuvenate and revitalize dry, tired skin, leaving it soft, supple, and radiant.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Panthenol (Vitamin B5): This skin-loving vitamin acts as a humectant, attracting and locking in moisture to keep your skin hydrated and smooth. Panthenol also helps to soothe and calm irritated skin, making it perfect for sensitive or dry skin types.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Sunflower Oil: Rich in vitamins A, D, and E, sunflower oil is a lightweight yet powerful emollient that nourishes and protects the skin. It absorbs quickly to replenish moisture and improve the overall texture and tone of your skin, leaving it feeling velvety soft and silky smooth.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Scented with sensual blend of skin safe fragrance oils, this butter will&nbsp;captivate your senses with&nbsp;a luxuriously soft, feminine, and delicately sweet fragrance that wraps your skin in pure indulgence.&nbsp;This enchanting blend opens with a&nbsp;whimsically elegant and&nbsp;light and airy aroma infused with delicate peony, soft jasmine, and sugared berries. As the fragrance settles, the warmth of creamy vanilla emerges, adding a buttery smoothness that lingers like the embrace of a cozy cashmere wrap.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>The result? A dreamy, romantic scent that is both playfully sweet and irresistibly comforting, leaving your skin beautifully scented and nourished all day long.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Indulge your senses and treat your skin to the ultimate hydration experience with our all natural Jamaican handmade&nbsp;Body Butter. Whether you use it as a daily moisturizer, post-shower treat, or before bed ritual, your skin will thank you for the loving care it deserves.</p>",
