    "description": "<p>Introducing our all natural body butter! Vanilla Bae, 4oz&nbsp;luxurious body butter formulated with the finest natural ingredients to nourish and pamper you from head to toe.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Kokum Butter: Known for its exceptional moisturizing properties, kokum butter is deeply hydrating without leaving a greasy residue. Packed with essential fatty acids and antioxidants, it helps to rejuvenate and revitalize dry, tired skin, leaving it soft, supple, and radiant.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Panthenol (Vitamin B5): This skin-loving vitamin acts as a humectant, attracting and locking in moisture to keep your skin hydrated and smooth. Panthenol also helps to soothe and calm irritated skin, making it perfect for sensitive or dry skin types.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Sunflower Oil: Rich in vitamins A, D, and E, sunflower oil is a lightweight yet powerful emollient that nourishes and protects the skin. It absorbs quickly to replenish moisture and improve the overall texture and tone of your skin, leaving it feeling velvety soft and silky smooth.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Indulge your senses and treat your skin to the ultimate hydration experience with our handcrafted Body Butter. Whether you use it as a daily moisturizer, post-shower treat, or before bed ritual, your skin will thank you for the loving care it deserves.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Scented with&nbsp;a tantalizing blend that captures the essence of pure, creamy vanilla.&nbsp;A&nbsp;classic scent, reminiscent of freshly baked vanilla desserts and homemade custard.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Immerse yourself in the irresistible allure of vanilla&nbsp;with our Vanilla Bae Body Butter today&nbsp;and let its amazing&nbsp;scent envelop you in pure delight.</p>",
